:

*Lepu* devojku je neko upoznao preko interneta. (He met a beautiful girl over the internet.)

*Lepa* je bila u njegovim očima. (She was beautiful in his eyes.)

*Lepo* se poigrala sa njim. (She played nicely with him.)

*Lepše* je bilo što mu je pokazala svoje pravo lice. (It was nicer that she showed him her true face.)

*Lepšim* je dolazila do njega. (She was coming to him in a more beautiful way.)

*Lepše* se osećala u njegovom prisustvu. (She felt better in his presence.)